cps.server.controllers

Interface CarTransportationController

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CarTransportationControllerA

    public interface CarTransportationController
    Is used to make it possible to swap out different insertion/retrieval algorithms. The insertion/retrieval algorithm is used to pack cars into the internal storage (parking cell array) of a parking lot.
